# Rule: Test Runners

Use the following runners:
- **Unit and integration tests**: pytest (`uv run pytest tests/`)
- **API view tests**: Django test client
- **Acceptance (end-to-end) tests**: Playwright via pytest (`uv run pytest tests/e2e/` from repo root; `tests/e2e/pytest.ini` disables the Playwright plugin so prefer root). **Full suite (BPE-07 / release gate)**: `uv run pytest tests/ tests/e2e/ -o addopts='--tb=short --strict-markers --reuse-db'`